description: “James asks the teacher about a Demon Sadhu,and goes to one brothel that is commanded by that person he’s searching for.He asks a prostitute to tell where he is.And he is Timothy Townsend the same man that killed his wife and was James colonel.After James is beaten by him,he returns to the professors home and plans to stop him.”

Wolverine Magazine #2 is a collection of four stories, all packed into one magazine sized comic. Included in the set are the following issues:

"Surprise!!" from Wolverine First Class #2

"The Bird, the Beast, and the Lizard" from X-Men First Class #2

"Second Genesis" from Giant-Size X-Men #1

"Cereal Quest" exclusive to this magazine, with the exciting conclusion to Wolverine's adventurous morning in search of his favorite breakfast cereal.

Also included is a Wolverine centerfold poster which depicts the regular cover of Wolverine Origins #1.
